==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forthink
<hw>For*think"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To repent; to
regret; to be sorry for; to cause regret.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧Let it <xex>forthink</xex> you.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Tyndale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That me <qex>forthinketh</qex>, quod this January.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forthputing</ent>⟦br⟧
